select COUNT(v_union_projets.idProjet) AS projet_nb, COALESCE(idEtp, idEtp_inter) AS idEtp, customers.customerName AS etp_name, `psc`.`idSubContractor`, `sub`.`customerName` as `sub_name` from `v_union_projets` left join `entreprises` on COALESCE(v_union_projets.idEtp, v_union_projets.idEtp_inter) = `entreprises`.`idCustomer` left join `customers` on `entreprises`.`idCustomer` = `customers`.`idCustomer` left join `project_forms` on `v_union_projets`.`idProjet` = `project_forms`.`idProjet` left join `formateurs` on `formateurs`.`idFormateur` = `project_forms`.`idFormateur` left join `project_sub_contracts` as `psc` on `v_union_projets`.`idProjet` = `psc`.`idProjet` left join `customers` as `sub` on `psc`.`idSubContractor` = `sub`.`idCustomer` where `headDate` is not null and (`idCfp_intra` = 2 or `idCfp_inter` = 2 or `psc`.`idSubContractor` = 2) and `project_is_trashed` = 0 group by COALESCE(idEtp, idEtp_inter) order by `etp_name` asc
